pageContext.claim: “They actually say we're going to quadruple to spend it on a Green New Deal, this ridiculous Green New Deal, which makes no sense, designed by AOC plus three, that had nothing to do, didn't even study the environment, now they're telling us, you know, about the Green New Deal.”
